; outline: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black;\">We are a professional and experienced integrated&nbsp; drill enterprise which engages in the design, research,development, manufacturing and marketing of different kinds of product in superior quality, competitive price and perfect service for more than 20 years</span></p>\r\n<p style=\";margin-bottom: 0; background: white; outline: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; color: #0070c0;\"><strong>Product Description</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #0070c0;\"><strong><br /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img title=\"FRD-W900 Meters Water Well Drilling Machine (2)\" src=\"/upload/product/1583411712652640.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img title=\"FRD-W900 Meters Water Well Drilling Machine\" src=\"/upload/product/1583411755473541.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\";margin-bottom: 0; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: \'Helvetica\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #333333;\">The rig\'s maximum drilling depth is up to 900 meters, the maximum hole diameter 105~445mm, can match the different application like geothermal projects, exploitation of groundwater, hydro-geological exploration, piling in foundation and some other projects.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\";margin-bottom: 0; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: \'Helvetica\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #333333;\">The whole machine is advantageous with a more powerful lifting, bigger output torque, higher working efficiency, flexibility, as well as better stability etc.,&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\";marg