	(177,'<p>Pakistani customers visited our company and discussed with us to open an exhibition hall in tube lifter.</p>','<p>&ldquo;Agricultural Internet of Things can implement farmland management and control through the comprehensive sensing of all the elements of agricultural production, including meteorology, soil, water, fertilizer, crop growth, etc., using methods such as big data transmission and intelligent learning to ensure the quality of agricultural products. Agriculture is highly productive and efficient.&rdquo; At the Agricultural Internet of Things Development Trend Forum held recently, Zhang Zhizhen, president of China Water Conservancy Enterprise Association, told reporters that at present, China\'s agriculture is in a critical period of transition from traditional agriculture to modern agriculture, using cloud computing and big data. Modern information technology such as mobile Internet transforms traditional agriculture and integrates various agricultural resources to effectively improve the comprehensive competitiveness and sustainable development capability of agriculture.</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img title=\"news_\" src=\"https://www.frdrillgroup.com/upload/news/1579265028730547.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Agricultural Internet of Things can implement farmland management and control through the comprehensive sensing of all the elements of agricultural production, including meteorology, soil, water, fertilizer, crop growth, etc., using methods such as big data transmission and intelligent learning to ensure the quality of agricultural products. Agriculture is highly productive and efficient.&rdquo; At the Agricultural Internet of Things Development Trend Forum held recently, Zhang Zhizhen, president of China Water Conservancy Enterprise Association, told reporters that at present, China\'s agriculture is in a critical period of transition from traditional agriculture to modern agriculture, using cloud computing and big data. Modern information technology such as mobile Internet traKang Shaozhong, an academician of the Chinese Academy of Engineering and an academician of the Jinglan Science and Technology Academician station, believes that the development of agricultural Internet of Things technology and smart agriculture is a necessary means for China to achieve agricultural modernization. \"China\'s labor productivity is low, rural labor is relatively lacking, and relying on the Internet of Things can be very good. Solve these problems.\"</p>\r\n<p>At present, the National IoT Regional Trial and Demonstration Project has been comprehensively promoted in 9 provinces, and the efficiency of cost-saving has been remarkable. The Ministry of Agriculture has released 426 items of Internet of Things technology products and models, and the information entry into the village is progressing. Cong Xiaoman, director of the Information System System Development Department of the Ministry of Agriculture, suggested that the promotion of the agricultural Internet of Things should be clear to the modern agriculture with Chinese characteristics. It is not possible to copy foreign large-scale machinery and large-scale agricultural models, and to plan based on China&rsquo;s national conditions. And advancement.</p>\r\n<p>Experts pointed out that it is necessary to closely focus on the main line of agricultural supply-side structural reform, to promote the balance of supply and demand of agricultural products with new technologies, and to optimize resource allocation. Use data as the core of building smart agriculture and deep integration of agricultural needs with IT technology. We must also give full play to the role of market players, especially farmers, and let farmers really benefit. Increase government investment, explore the establishment of enterprises as a mechanism for investment and research and development, and form a pattern of coordinated promotion by governments, scientific research institutions, enterprises and farmers.</p>'),
	(178,'<p>Bellows compensator, also called the expansion section, or the expansion section. Composed of a corrugated pipe (an elastic element) and an end pipe, a bracket, a flange, a pipe, etc.. Mainly used in a variety of pipe, it can compensate the thermal displacement of the pipeline, mechanical deformation and absorb a variety of mechanical vibration, play a role in reducing the pipe deformation stress and improve the service life of the pipeline, can also be used for noise reduction.</p>','<p>Bellows compensator, also called the expansion section, or the expansion section. Composed of a corrugated pipe (an elastic element) and an end pipe, a bracket, a flange, a pipe, etc.. Mainly used in a variety of pipe, it can compensate the thermal displacement of the pipeline, mechanical deformation and absorb a variety of mechanical vibration, play a role in reducing the pipe deformation stress and improve the service life of the pipeline, can also be used for noise reduction. The corrugated compensator is divided into two kinds of flange connection and welding. Buried pipe compensator commonly used welding methods. Working principle: Corrugated compensator is used to use corrugated compensator of the elastic component of the effective expansion deformation to absorb pipeline, pipe or container by thermal expansion and contraction, causes the size change of a compensation device, which belongs to a compensating element. Absorption of axial, lateral, and angular displacement.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Common type:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1, hzN (ZN) Example: 0.6TNY500TF Said: the nominal diameter of &Phi; 500, the working pressure is 0.6MPa. (6kg/cm2) wavenumber for 4, with a draft tube, carbon steel flange connection of inner pressure corrugated compensator.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2, hzw (ZW) Example: 0.6TWY500&times; 8JB Said: nominal diameter is 500mm, the working pressure is 0.6MPa (6kg/cm2) wavenumber for eight, stainless steel pipe connection type axial type corrugated compensator. Note: the setting of the trap is required by the user.</p>\r\n<p>3, axial compound ripple compensator (ZF) Example: 0.6FS100&times; 20F Said: working pressure is 0.6MPa, through the DN=100mm, the wave number is 20, the flange is connected with a double type corrugated compensator.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>4, axial compound tension rod corrugated compensator (FL) Example: 0.6FSL200&times; 12J Said: working pressure is 0.6MPa, through the DN=200mm, the wave number is 12, the connection of the composite rod.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>5, buried in the pressure compensator (ZMNY) Example: 1.6ZMS200&times; 6J Said: working pressure of 1.6Mpa, nominal diameter of 200mm, wavenumber for six waves, take over the connection of the buried &amp; gt; corrugated compensator.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>6, universal hinge bellows compensator (WJ) Example: 0.6WJY500&times; 4F The working pressure is 0.6MPa, the nominal diameter is 500mm, the wave number is 4, and the carbon steel flange is connected with the universal hinge.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>7, straight pipe pressure balance type corrugated compensator (ZP) Example: 0.6ZYP500&times; 8/6-JB Nominal diameter is 500, the working pressure is 0.6MPa, the big corrugated pipe is 8 wave, the small corrugated pipe is 16 wave, the connection form is the stainless steel tube pressure balance type corrugated compensator.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>8, curved pipe pressure balance type corrugated compensator Example: 0.25QYP700&times; 8/4JB Said: nominal diameter is &phi; 700mm, the working pressure 0.25Mpa, the wave number is 8/4, the stainless steel pipe is connected with the curved pipe pressure balance type corrugated compensator&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>9, internal and external pressure balance type corrugated compensator (NP) Example: 1.6NP200*8j Said: working pressure is 1.6Mpa, through the DN=200mm, the wave number is 8, the internal and external pressure balance type bellows.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>10, metal flexible compensator (FJ) Example: (1) FXDA4500&times; 4000F400 Said square non metal compensator, long-term work &le; 100, the inner wall is 4500&times; 4000mm, flange connection, product length 400mm (2) YXDB800F250 Circular non metallic compensator, long working &le; 200, the inner diameter of DN800mm, the flange connection of the compensator, the length of 250mm More hardware products to buy, please exchange a purchase.</p>'),
	(180,'<p>First: when starting the motor does not rotate when the micro pump. Reason: 1 auxiliary switch DC regulated power supply fault; 2 battery or battery without power is not enough; 3 line contact; 4 motor and carbon brush contact; Second: after the start of the pump motor work but not the water.</p>','<p>First: when starting the motor does not rotate when the micro pump.<br /><br />Reason:<br />1 auxiliary switch DC regulated power supply fault;<br />2 battery or battery without power is not enough;<br />3 line contact;<br />4 motor and carbon brush contact; Second: after the start of the pump motor work but not the water.<br /><br />Reason:<br />1 there are debris or particulate impurities in the pump;<br />2 suction process is higher than the pump rated suction process; Third: traffic shortage. Reason: 1 the actual head of the pump more than the allowable lift; 2 voltage is too low, the motor speed is slow;<br />3 suction process is too high;<br />4 air entry into the pipe; Fourth: the flow gradually become small.<br /><br />Reason:<br />1 water inlet impurities blocked;<br />2 filter use time is too long, there is a particle impurity; Fifth: the work of the micro pump water abnormal interrupt.<br /><br />Reason:<br />1 motor does not start, the exclusion of circuit fault;<br />2 pipe plug, remove plug;<br />3 pipeline rupture, repair welding or replacement;<br />4 strainer plug, plug removal;<br />5 water outlet pipe exposed surface; Sixth: the pump is running at the time of violent vibration or noise abnormal increase.<br /><br />Reason:<br />1 access voltage higher than the set voltage;<br />2 mounting angle is not fixed;<br />3 motor or pump shaft bending.</p>');
